43:18.972 --> 43:20.765
Give me that.

43:20.807 --> 43:23.560
It belonged to your grandfather.

43:23.601 --> 43:25.562
Wait, you m...

43:26.813 --> 43:28.398
Wait...

43:28.440 --> 43:31.026
Oh, hi.

44:24.913 --> 44:27.290
Are you okay?

44:27.332 --> 44:30.460
What's the matter? The hora spun
the roast in your stomach?

44:32.295 --> 44:34.255
What?

44:34.297 --> 44:37.342
- I get it.
- You get what?

44:37.384 --> 44:41.346
My safta always wanted me
to feel...

44:42.931 --> 44:44.641
part of our people.

44:47.644 --> 44:49.020
Part of our tribe.

44:51.106 --> 44:52.357
L'chaim.

44:52.399 --> 44:54.442
I just need a minute.

44:54.484 --> 44:55.693
L'chaim.

44:59.406 --> 45:01.241
♪ ♪

45:01.282 --> 45:02.617
- Murray.
- What?

45:02.659 --> 45:05.245
I heard what you said.

45:05.286 --> 45:07.264
What'd I say? I don't know
what you're talking about.

45:07.288 --> 45:09.290
30 years, I...

45:09.332 --> 45:14.254
I have not heard you say
that word: "Amen."

45:14.295 --> 45:17.424
What?

45:17.465 --> 45:20.176
A person can't be thankful?

45:23.763 --> 45:25.765
