45:35.567 --> 45:37.694
Congratulations!

45:38.903 --> 45:41.656
♪ I can't believe... ♪

45:43.658 --> 45:46.619
♪ My baby done put me down... ♪

45:46.661 --> 45:50.206
I got a name. Tim Randall.
That's The Ghost's alias.

45:50.248 --> 45:51.767
Which means we've got
a way to track him.

45:51.791 --> 45:53.418
Mazel tov.

45:53.460 --> 45:56.671
Jews, Jewesses,
great to see my people.

45:56.713 --> 45:58.798
Oh, hello, hello, hello, hello.

45:58.840 --> 46:01.259
How are you?
Good to see you.

46:01.301 --> 46:04.137
Oh, what can I say?
The fans love me.

46:04.179 --> 46:06.973
- Yeah. Did you find out
anything from the book?
- Yeah.

46:07.015 --> 46:08.975
It's some, uh,
"Are You There, God?

46:09.017 --> 46:10.393
It's Me, Adolf" shit.

46:10.435 --> 46:11.936
It's like an instruction manual.

46:11.978 --> 46:13.646
They're starting a war, Meyer.

46:13.688 --> 46:14.898
They're trying to...

46:14.939 --> 46:16.625
I think they're trying
to create a Fourth Reich.

46:16.649 --> 46:18.610
Ugh.

46:26.784 --> 46:27.952
No, Joe.
What's he doing?

46:27.994 --> 46:29.204
What? What?

46:29.245 --> 46:30.246
Mazel tov!

46:30.288 --> 46:33.166
You fucking liar.

46:33.208 --> 46:34.792
No, not here, Joe!

46:34.834 --> 46:36.419
No. Come, in there.

46:36.461 --> 46:38.301
- In there.
