gift, you bloody idiot.

46:40.632 --> 46:42.926
- Shut up.
- What the...?

46:42.967 --> 46:44.761
- Stop!
- You fucking...

46:44.802 --> 46:46.846
Stop.

46:46.888 --> 46:49.015
That's the second time today
some twat has tried me.

46:49.057 --> 46:50.767
You fucking traitor.

46:50.808 --> 46:53.436
Get outside and open
the fucking trunk!

46:55.563 --> 46:57.148
Who the fuck is that?

46:59.275 --> 47:02.779
- Is that The Wolf?
- Not my Wolf.

47:02.820 --> 47:05.698
Harriet, do not deliver

47:05.740 --> 47:09.035
your gift till after
the wedding. Joe.

47:09.077 --> 47:12.455
You got a lead, right? Cool off.

47:12.497 --> 47:15.583
Go chase your lead down.
Go ahead.

47:15.625 --> 47:16.793
Let's go, man.

47:16.834 --> 47:18.086
Come on.

47:18.127 --> 47:19.879
Um, hey. I-I-I need
to ask you something.

47:19.921 --> 47:22.006
- No, Jonah, not now, please.
- No, but just can...

47:22.048 --> 47:24.634
You need to go, Jonah. Go.

47:24.676 --> 47:26.678
Do it another time.

47:43.861 --> 47:45.613
Where did you find him?

47:45.655 --> 47:47.132
Oh, there's a lovely
little gift store

47:47.156 --> 47:49.242
in Alabama.

47:49.284 --> 47:51.828
Turns out those rednecks
are good for something.

47:54.205 --> 47:56.708
Well, is it true
what they are telling me?

47:56.749 --> 48:00.670
