upon yourself to kill others

48:00.712 --> 48:03.840
without proper verification?

48:03.881 --> 48:06.092
We have a code.

48:08.761 --> 48:09.929
A code?

48:09.971 --> 48:11.681
Do we, Meyer?

48:13.474 --> 48:15.393
Or is that just something
we tell ourselves,

48:15.435 --> 48:18.438
so we can believe we're not like
the monsters we hunt?

48:22.317 --> 48:24.902
