48:24.944 --> 48:26.613
but not like them.

48:26.654 --> 48:29.490
We have an excuse.

48:31.618 --> 48:34.454
War created us.

49:25.922 --> 49:27.590
Good morning, Sister.

49:27.632 --> 49:30.051
Good morning, child.

49:30.093 --> 49:33.596
It's...

49:33.638 --> 49:35.431
Harriet.

49:35.473 --> 49:37.517
Grant us Thy salvation.

50:00.665 --> 50:02.667
