50:56.679 --> 50:58.848
I said I'm fine! Stop.

51:05.938 --> 51:10.067
Listen, um, I've been thinking,

51:10.109 --> 51:14.906
uh, you know, this "us" thing is
my first serious relationship,

51:14.947 --> 51:17.950
and I...

51:19.786 --> 51:23.790
When we first met, I...
I wanted to take things slow

51:23.831 --> 51:26.167
