ready for something serious,

51:26.209 --> 51:28.336
and you wanted to rush in,
and I just...

51:28.377 --> 51:30.421
- Don't fucking do this.
- I don't think this...

51:30.463 --> 51:33.633
- This is bullshit.
- I want some space.

51:33.674 --> 51:36.761
- Things moved too fast for me...
- You're a liar. Space?

51:36.803 --> 51:39.639
That's the best
you could come up with?

51:39.680 --> 51:41.057
I don't believe you.

51:41.098 --> 51:44.018
Well, maybe we just want
different things.

51:45.812 --> 51:47.230
Why are you doing this?

51:49.732 --> 51:51.734
Why are you fucking doing this?

51:53.611 --> 51:55.988
I'm telling you the truth.

51:56.030 --> 51:57.657
Bullshit.

51:59.659 --> 52:01.369
What is it? You're scared?

52:05.414 --> 52:06.999
I don't want to do this.

52:07.041 --> 52:09.460
I want to do this.
I'm doing this.

52:19.136 --> 52:22.139
Fuck you, Millie Morris.

52:22.181 --> 52:26.143
You... you love me,
and you know you love me,

52:26.185 --> 52:28.604
and I know you're full of shit!

52:51.669 --> 52:55.006
-I loved the singing.
-I just want to sleep.
