52:55.047 --> 52:57.925
- I think it went great.
- Can't we... I want
to lie next to you.

52:57.967 --> 53:00.767
- I want to think
about nothing. I want...
- But what I want to do is...

53:02.555 --> 53:04.932
Oh, d-don't be alarmed.

53:04.974 --> 53:08.311
You realize you
shouldn't surprise old people.

53:08.352 --> 53:09.562
- Hmm?
- Yeah.

53:14.191 --> 53:16.652
Your wedding gift
is in the basement.

53:16.694 --> 53:20.072
Oh, oh, really? For Amy?

53:20.114 --> 53:22.116
No, no.

53:22.158 --> 53:25.202
No. This one's just for you.

54:07.411 --> 54:09.413
♪ ♪

54:19.799 --> 54:21.008
No.

54:23.386 --> 54:25.388
Oh...

54:57.795 --> 55:00.256
Back door?

